[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-13T21:40:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/ebc37845e564070fa4f2c756c1491123.jpg\" /><p>For years now, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/bloodborne-the-kotaku-review-1695227854\">Bloodborne</a> fans have wanted the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/bloodborne-remastered-ps5-nibellion-fromsoftware-elden-1848995544\">popular PS4-exclusive RPG</a> <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/you-can-play-bloodborne-on-pc-using-ps-now-1828909625\">ported to PC</a>, hopefully with performance improvements and graphical options. And while FromSoftware\u2019s president Hidetaka Miyazaki didn\u2019t confirm that such a port is happening, he did say he\u2019s not opposed to it and suggested that many people at\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/bloodborne-pc-port-ps5-fromsoftware-elden-ring-miyazaki-1851539098\">Read more...</a></p", "id": 708881, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/bloodborne-pc-port-ps5-fromsoftware-elden-ring-miyazaki-1851539098", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/ebc37845e564070fa4f2c756c1491123.jpg", "title": "FromSoftware's Miyazaki On A Bloodborne PC Port: 'I'd Love More Players To Be Able To Enjoy It'", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-13T21:30:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/de84730918b84dd2ea150297c131b3ca.jpg\" /><p>Disney Plus\u2019 latest Star Wars series, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/the-acolyte-disney-plus-kotor-kreia-1851525694\">The Acolyte</a>, was always going to court controversy. The Star Wars fandom has an infamously vocal minority who are, for lack of a better term, bigots, and <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/star-wars-racism-sexism-acolyte-fan-backlash-kennedy-1851511756\">Lucasfilm had already promised to stand up</a> to them ahead of the series\u2019 launch. But after The Acolyte episode 3, an entirely\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/star-wars-the-acolyte-episode-3-witches-brendok-jedi-1851539149\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 708882, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/star-wars-the-acolyte-episode-3-witches-brendok-jedi-1851539149", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/de84730918b84dd2ea150297c131b3ca.jpg", "title": "Star Wars: The Acolyte Tells Us What We Already Knew About The Jedi", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-13T21:10:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/8bce15e9aba1d577b6a9a56896f6191c.jpg\" /><p>When the action-adventure game <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/neva\">Neva</a> was first revealed a year ago with a <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/ps5-playstation-showcase-neva-trailer-gameplay-1850471819\">trailer