he real Yasuke was\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-yasuke-backlash-racist-elon-1851539007\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 708884, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-yasuke-backlash-racist-elon-1851539007", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/76fa78cc76b7538546189a12d1bf9ed3.jpg", "title": "Assassin\u2019s Creed Shadows Producer Responds To Backlash Over Yasuke", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-13T20:20:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/ac404eb20808a526392c53c117a4557f.jpg\" /><p>Summer is looking stacked with <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/sgf-2024-summer-game-fest-ubisoft-xbox-best-trailers-1851532597\">big and small game releases across all platforms</a>. If you were hoping you\u2019d get a break from all the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/summer-game-fest-day-devs-indie-showcase-retro-ufo50-1851527297\">awesome games launching this year</a> in the hotter months of 2024, I\u2019ve got bad news for you and your wallet.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/summer-game-release-dates-indies-star-wars-w40k-2024-1851538599\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 708494, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/summer-game-release-dates-indies-star-wars-w40k-2024-1851538599", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "so