}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-13T19:58:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/4120d1df7dc9b4b991128c0e95c71936.jpg\" /><p>Apparently it\u2019s update day in the world of current-gen consoles. The <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://howl.me/cmsn24Z3Aid\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" target=\"_blank\">PlayStation 5</a> is finally getting direct Discord integration and other improvements, while the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://howl.me/cmsn3x3z63T\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" target=\"_blank\">Xbox Series X</a>/<a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://howl.me/cmsn364sdew\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" target=\"_blank\">S</a> address dynamic background and Wi-Fi password frustrations. This is the lowkey console UX war we love to see. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/ps5-discord-xbox-controller-disconnect-wi-fi", "id": 708496, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/ps5-discord-xbox-controller-disconnect-wi-fi-update-1851538776", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/4120d1df7dc9b4b991128c0e95c71936.jpg", "title": "New Updates Just Made The PS5 And Xbox Series X/S A Little Better", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-13T17:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/cdfc73754285b82